:R-HSA-8948747  a           owl:NamedIndividual , obo:GO_0008150 ;
        rdfs:comment        "When monoubiquitinated by E3 ubiquitin ligases XIAP and NEDD4, PTEN translocates from the cytosol to the nucleus (Trotman et al. 2007, Van Themsche et al. 2009). USP7 (HAUSP)-mediated deubiquitination of monoubiquitinated nuclear PTEN promotes relocalization of PTEN to the cytosol (Song et al. 2008)." ;
        rdfs:label          "Regulation of PTEN localization" ;
        dc:contributor      "Authored: Carracedo, Arkaitz, 2016-08-11" , "Authored: Salmena, Leonardo, 2016-08-11" , "Authored: Orlic-Milacic, Marija, 2016-11-16" , "Reviewed: Matthews, Lisa, 2025-02-26" , "Edited: Orlic-Milacic, Marija, 2017-05-09" , "GOC:reactome_curators" ;
        dc:date             "2026-06-29" ;
